BRUTALIST DESIGN RULES
Black, white, and yellow color scheme
No rounded corners
We use tailwind v4 and daisy UI the max we can, we design bold and brutalist design with main color black and white and highlight yellow

To create new database migration do `supabase migration new [NAME]`
To migrate the database you created do `supabase db push --local`
To create db test do `supabase test new `
Test your RLS, and functions
To run db test do `supabase db test`
To reset the db after some test, do `supabase db reset`
You are not allowed to restart supabase it take too much time

To update supabase type run bun run gen:types:local after db reset
Keep components small and focused
Maximum 50 lines per component
Single responsibility principle
Explicit props with default values
Clear naming conventions
use bun and bunx not npm and node
Code DRY and make sure the code 
Align the happy path to the left edge
